=== 出现于其他游戏 ===

*2009年世嘉发行《[[魔兵驚天錄|魔兵驚天錄]]》（[[Platinum_Games|Platinum Games]]开发）冲破火网的音乐作为重混出現在第8章《道路666》中<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gamesradar.com/f/30-hidden-references-in-bayonetta/a-2010011493658559064|title=30 'hidden' references in Bayonetta|last=Reparaz|first=Mikel|date=January 14, 2010|work=GamesRadar UK|accessdate=November 8, 2010|archive-date=2011-06-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110615185748/http://www.gamesradar.com/f/30-hidden-references-in-bayonetta/a-2010011493658559064|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
*2012年竞速游戏《[[索尼克全明星赛车_变形|索尼克全明星赛车 变形]]》一个关卡基于《冲破火网》F-14雄猫亦是解锁角色AGES的飞行器<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.tssznews.com/2012/11/14/first-video-shows-the-latest-unlockable-of-sonic-all-stars-racing-transformed/ |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2014-08-20 |archive-date=2014-08-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140821105515/http://www.tssznews.com/2012/11/14/first-video-shows-the-latest-unlockable-of-sonic-all-stars-racing-transformed/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

